helakatha (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of HelaKatha - Singlish to Sinhala Input Tool
  * Phonetic Singlish to Sinhala Unicode transliteration
  * Global keyboard hook with candidate window
  * Clipboard-based Unicode injection
  * System tray integration and autostart support
  * Unicode and Legacy (FM Abhaya) font modes
  * Draggable language switcher bar

